creator: pierre.delisle@sun.com
text:
submitted by Kan Ogawa (super-creek@jcom.home.ne.jp)
I found some minor typos in standard-examples web application,
so I will submit the patch. Can you apply it before Standard Tablib 1.0.3 will 
be released?

Pierre:
Patch fixes the following typos/omissions:
- examples/web/index.html: added link to the new TLV tests
- web/import/links.html: <param> instead of <param>
- web/tlv/index.html: typo 
     PerittedTaglibsError.jsp -> PermittedTaglibsError.jsp
Thanks for the report! These have now been fixed.
creator: pierre.delisle@sun.com
